Summary of Commands
Here's a quick summary of the commands for your reference:

Start CDH: ./StartCDH.sh
Check Java Processes: jps
Stop CDH: ./StopCDH.sh
Create Directory in HDFS: hdfs dfs -mkdir /user/hadoop/jeev
Create/Edit File (vi): vi textfile.txt
Create/Edit File (nano): nano sample.txt
Upload File to HDFS: hdfs dfs -put sample.txt /user/hadoop/Ramya
Download File from HDFS: hdfs dfs -get /user/hadoop/Ramya/sample.txt
Display File Content: hdfs dfs -cat /user/hadoop/Ramya/sample.txt
Remove File from HDFS: hdfs dfs -rm /user/hadoop/Ramya/sample.txt
Copy File in HDFS: hdfs dfs -cp /user/hadoop/Ramya/sample.txt /user/hadoop/jeev/sample.txt
Move File in HDFS: hdfs dfs -mv /user/hadoop/Ramya/sample.txt /user/hadoop/jeev/sample.txt
